@startuml sequence_report_submission
!include _thesis_style.puml

actor "Warga Pelapor" as User
participant "SmartCityApps\n(Android Client)" as App
participant "FastAPI Backend\n/predict" as Backend
participant "Inference Module\nDINOv3 + mE5 + CatBoost+PGS" as Inference
participant "Nearest Agency\nRouting Service" as Routing
database "Supabase\nDB + Storage" as Supabase
participant "Petugas Instansi" as Officer

User -> App : Isi deskripsi,\nambil foto,\nizinkan lokasi
App -> App : Capture latitude + longitude
App -> Backend : POST /predict (HTTP)\nimage + laporan + lat/lon

Backend -> Backend : Validate request
Backend -> Inference : Preprocess image + text\nrun multiclass inference
Inference --> Backend : predicted class,\nconfidence,\nall probabilities
Backend -> Routing : predicted class + lat/lon
Routing --> Backend : nearest agency,\ndistance meters
Backend --> App : JSON prediction,\nconfidence, assignment

App -> User : Tampilkan hasil AI,\nconfidence, instansi terdekat
User -> App : Konfirmasi atau koreksi kategori
App -> Supabase : Upload report image
App -> Supabase : Insert reports row:\nprediction + assignment + status
Supabase --> App : Saved report id

Officer -> App : Ubah status ke resolved/selesai
App -> Supabase : Upload resolution evidence photo
App -> Supabase : RPC update_report_status\nphoto_url + note
Supabase --> App : Resolved report + audit trail

note over App,Backend
SmartCityApps acts as client only.
The ML model is not executed on Android.
end note

@enduml
